# Description:
#   Execute a top command on a condor job
#
# Usage:
#  glidein_top.py <cluster>.<process> [-name <schedd_name>] [-pool <pool_name> ] [-timeout <nr secs>]
#
# Author:
#   Igor Sfiligoi (May 2007)
#
# License:
#  Fermitools
